<item>
            <title>[LU-1063] speed up kms recalculation</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1063</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;with the patch above the kms value calculated more quickly because of next improvements:&lt;br/&gt;
1) interval tree was used for the going through the list of locks instead the direct linked list&lt;br/&gt;
search.&lt;br/&gt;
2) skip the subtree when maximum value in this subtree is less then new kms&lt;br/&gt;
3) kms search stopped when lock with size equal to the old kms value found.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;this optimization shows speed increase from 20 to 40% according to the tests results.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=22060&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=22060&lt;/a&gt; - contains the whole story&lt;/p&gt;</description>
